# PR resolution

When working on PR feedback or CI failures:

- Iterate until checks are green.
- Resolve or reply to every inline review thread.
- **After each push to the PR branch, run `sleep 600` (10 minutes) before polling checks and review threads again** so CodeRabbit/Bugbot/Copilot can finish — do not declare “done” immediately after push. See `.claude/agents/pr-resolution-follow-up.md`.
- Use **GraphQL `reviewThreads`** (`isResolved`) to detect unresolved conversations; REST pull comments alone are insufficient.
- Do not introduce secrets or unrelated refactors.
- Follow `.claude/agents/pr-resolution-follow-up.md` for the full loop.
